parameters.name: R
parameters.description: Distance of Pioneer 11 from Jupiter, in Jupiter RADII (1 Jupiter radii is 71372 KM).

parameters.name: LAT
parameters.description: Latitude of Pioneer 11 in System III (1957.0), measured from the equotor, positive northward.

parameters.name: LON
parameters.description: Longitude of Pioneer 11 in System III (1957.0), west longitude.

parameters.name: BR
parameters.description: Radial component of the magnetic field in RJ coordinates, positive away from Jupiter.

parameters.name: BTHETA
parameters.description: Polar component of the magnetic field in RJ coordinates, positive northward.

parameters.name: BPHI
parameters.description: Azimuthal component of the magnetic field in RJ coordinates, positive eastward.
